flightsim.simconnect.recv
Interface FacilitiesListHandler

public interface FacilitiesListHandler

The handler interface for receiving facilities list. For a more convenient use, all types of facilities are received through the same handler interface. For instance, requesting an VOR list will result in the call of the handleVORList(SimConnect, RecvVORList) method only.
